{"tid":292080,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"唔經唔覺方皓玟係2017年已經出左兩首新歌","createTime":"2017-06-21T05:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T18:05:15.000Z","uid":9030,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"516e29ffbf97c74b9da8bffbe7d72bcbdbea7d18","tid":292080,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"年頭忙電影同宣傳, 入左金像獎女配角五強, 之後即刻重投音樂<br />\n<br />\n4月出既COMMON SENSE , 個MV仲要素顏拍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UiD-O3gHBw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUiD-O3gHBw4&d=8eAG5A1w8i1IXExU1jg3cNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=80f6547b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UiD-O3gHBw4</a><br />\n<br />\n6月出既Let's Say, 請左好多有d名氣既演員拍, eg游學修, 陳家樂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TxjiHQcpXv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTxjiHQcpXv4&d=8eAG5A1w8i1IXExU1jg3cNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b0e30fb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TxjiHQcpXv4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前小明話10月會係StarHall開2場concert, 同埋今年會出碟......<br />\n以佢上隻碟10首都plug既玩法, 加埋Believe In Live, 終於好天氣, 還要去過生活已經有5首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9e293471e351104907ee1733b294b4664697db","tid":292080,"uid":591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"uwillc應該都會放埋入碟"},{"pid":"b4ef13c07f6b9eae96a622b15ab8d55c788d7221","tid":292080,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>uwillc應該都會放埋入碟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fa578013eb134c3dcce75616dff73c938f7fcb","tid":292080,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"方皓玟新歌嘆供樓苦 游學修被摑10 take：導演純粹想打我<br />\n方皓玟推出新歌《Let's Say》，今次題材繼續貼地寫實，講買樓嘅悲哀：「買樓你想買樓，買到也不見得享受」，諷刺為供樓失去自我嘅香港人。<br />\n今次個MV亦係亮點之一，客串演員幾乎雲集近年嘅新生代主力男星，包括游學修、《幸運是我》陳家樂、《點五步》林耀聲、《同囚》岑珈其、麥子樂、盧鎮業(小野)、何啟華（華Dee）等，有睇開港產片嘅影迷表示，見到個MV非常感動。<br />\n有份演出MV嘅游學修爆料指，導演臨收工想拍攝被人真摑一巴嘅鏡頭，游學修自願上陣被摑，拍咗大約10個take，點知最後竟然冇用到，笑指懷疑導演係純粹想打佢！"},{"pid":"09c158af7dd1c5518b92664f854094737cc8c362","tid":292080,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>uwillc應該都會放埋入碟</blockquote><br />\n等咗依首好耐<br />\n上次唔放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88524840498378305d14bb7d28571ad412b046aa","tid":292080,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"7-8/10 starhall"},{"pid":"45951d0dd9999b1cc71ed136a78c0f17bd3d3cd9","tid":292080,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7-8/10 starhall</blockquote><br />\n葛民輝監制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}